		//
		// description:
		//  Supports 5 formats for IPv4: dotted decimal, dotted hex, dotted octal, decimal and hexadecimal.
		//  Supports 2 formats for Ipv6.
		//
		// flags  An object.  All flags are boolean with default = true.
